		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=97459"><span id=Guru>Warric</span></a><b><span id=Guru><br>Guru</span></b><br><img src=/shared/user_star_ico.gif height=9 width=9><img src=/shared/user_star_ico.gif height=9 width=9><br>316 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.50]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Warric&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>As to spending your starting points on Stamina, the general concensus these days seems to be that Stamina is the way to go because the items that raise this stat appear to be less common than gear that enchances the other stats, Strength included.<br><br>These guys, <a href=HTTP://eq.crgaming.com/creationguides/Warrior.asp target=akztarg><b>Casters Realm -- Warrior Creation Guide</b></a>, once advocated putting starting points into Agility and Dexterity, for example, when starting an Ogre Warrior, and all into Strength for other races, some into Strength and the rest into Stamina for other races, etc.&nbsp;&nbsp;As you can see, they have since modified their position on this sometimes controversial issue.<br><br>As to whether to shoot for stats-enhancing gear or raw AC, there are some who say that AC is King and spending on anything else is foolish.  There are, of course, other opinions, and in the end it all comes down to what you want to do and how you want to play.  Here's another link to Allakhazam's Class-Specific Sites page:  <a href=HTTP://links.allakhazam.com/Everquest/Class_Specific_Sites/Warrior/index.html target=akztarg><b>Warrior</b></a>.  You should be able to easily get the answers you seek through there.<br><br>Good luck in whatever you decide.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Mar  4 16:58:32 2003</em></p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=613166 target=akztarg><b>Sunshatter Gobsmack -- Children of the Grave</b></a><br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=548619 target=akztarg><b>Djimn Rowanwood -- Dragonchow</b></a><br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=550239 target=akztarg><b>Khoush Bloodeyes</b></a></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >1 Replies</td></tr></table><table width="100%"><tr><td class=mhback>&nbsp;</td><td class=mhback >Thread Subject</a></td><td class=mhback>Started by</a></td><td class=mhback>Replies</a></td><td class=mhback>Last Post</a></td><td class=mhback>Rating</a></td></tr><tr class=mdr>
